---
title: Lemon Sugar Brioche French Toast with Honey-Baked Fruit & Cherry Sauce | Serves 2
description: Skip the café queue and add some sweetness to brunch time with our lemon sugar brioche French toast. Stack it high with cherry
sauce and honey-baked fruit, then top with whipped cream and pistachios for a decadent dish worth savouring.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/lemon-sugar-brioche-french-toast-a2287c2a.jpg
